{"tid":385847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【當年今日：皇家香港軍團1995年9月3日解散】","createTime":"2017-09-03T13:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T14:16:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1dfade0d506999040294fb9e8d317293b3454eb","tid":385847,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/21248329_1819973611363342_5995623842057003626_o.jpg?oh=785befb2d96530770adc154c110f261a&amp;oe=5A56CF48\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F21248329_1819973611363342_5995623842057003626_o.jpg%3Foh%3D785befb2d96530770adc154c110f261a%26oe%3D5A56CF48&h=bd36345c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n皇家香港軍團（義勇軍）的成立可追溯至1854年5月，當年由於克里米亞戰爭，駐港皇家海軍需要短暫離開香港，前往歐洲戰場服役，為了兼顧活躍於大鵬灣、伶仃洋及南中國海一帶的海盜，香港政府徵召香港志願人士組織「義勇軍（The Hong Kong Volunteers）」部隊，其名稱及編制在隨後百多年屢有更迭。至1970年，獲賜皇家名銜成皇家香港軍團（義勇軍）。<br />\n<br />\n義勇軍早年參與者多為居港英籍或外籍人士，後來則加入了不少華人。經過逾一個世紀的演進，義勇軍成為一專業且具高度機動性的部隊，也配備了先進的輕型武器；而香港演藝界人士鄧梓峰，曾加入此部隊，軍階至中尉。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提是，這支志願隊伍參與過1941年的香港保衞戰，六七暴動時也執行過內部保安工作，同時亦曾協助阻截非法入境者及維持越南船民營保安等，在防衞香港及維護香港治安中作出過極大的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n隨着香港政權快將易手、英治即將在1997年結束，部隊於95年9月3日正式解散。"},{"pid":"1088b858cbed70a0d382d980f8232c72ad4c32e0","tid":385847,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c004259bd28e5773b0f7e8b99d08cf1345d09a","tid":385847,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ba6cda18065cc2dd29f4eeabe71c2ad1523654","tid":385847,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:53:23.000Z","msg":"Salute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0ff42efc4b9799d35d04bfa4aecacb5c429661","tid":385847,"uid":3659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"真正義勇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa7ca124daf62e922a13e9ed47cfb17dd1b96ba","tid":385847,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"nulli secundus in oriente"},{"pid":"ed0921ba05e174b2d8483a26d5034de5c5087d3f","tid":385847,"uid":1080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"鄧 sir~~"},{"pid":"c107dc54748584af6e48b02c21972126a0442b44","tid":385847,"uid":13450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r3HsLTai5dQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr3HsLTai5dQ&d=RKd7FSYzb7Hpi5FCrb8Kuv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=a24836c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r3HsLTai5dQ</a><br />\n皇家香港軍團（義勇軍）解散前最後一次反偷渡行動 - (鄧梓峰中尉)(1995年)"},{"pid":"03985f352e1cdfb5fad819e01a5531634998d3d4","tid":385847,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19629eed48ea61b911f9e966a2f04f27c177d101","tid":385847,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}